                  units are micrograms per cubic meter of air (&mu;g/m<sup>3</sup>). To toggle between the two scales, simply
                  tap the center of the Speck's screen. The chart here details the measurement scale ranges and correlation between
                  value and color.  The Speck can also display colors in a blue-red palette for colorblind users.
               </p>
